func main() {
	list := &List{}
	list.add(1)
	list.add(2)
	list.add(3)
	list.add(4)
 
	println("Initial List: ")
	printList(list)
 
	list.remove(2)
	println("List after removing 2: ")
	printList(list)
 
	list.remove(4)
	println("List after removing 4: ")
	printList(list)
}
